name: She & Her Darling Ghost
description: When I tell them I'm going to photograph them, they hurry to strike a posture. More than that, they feel obligated to smile. Even if she was abandoned by the man she was supposed to marry when she discovered she was pregnant... She will spend her pregnancy on an island for 9 months, away from her friends and family. And she will find herself in a series of unsuccessful romances. She will, however, be a good mother since everyone with a womb has been trained how to be a good mother.
